Immerse yourself in a serene and enchanting anime scene with the Neko Anime Girl In The Rain Live Wallpaper. Perfect for anime enthusiasts who love tranquil moments!

🌐 Customizable search bar to use your preferred search engine.

🔗 Quick-access shortcuts for easy navigation to your favorite websites.
Add a touch of anime magic to your browsing experience and enjoy this calm, rain-filled aesthetic every time you open a new tab.
